title: PM, NA Speaker discuss legislative matters
content:
ISLAMABAD, June 14 (APP): Speaker National Assembly Asad Qaiser called on Prime Minister Imran Khan here on Monday and discussed the issues of importance.
The matters relating to parliament and legislation came under discussion, the PM Office said.
